metadata.name: LINKED Collectors Pass #1
metadata.description: The LINKED Collectors Pass gives you early access to LINK NFT drops in the LINKED collection. The more you mint, the greater the utility. You can burn this pass during the minting of a LINK NFT for a 50% discount - just like exchanging a gift voucher during a store checkout. For a full breakdown of utility, visit https://mhouse.club/linked-collectors-pass
